hadiths[70]{hadithnumber,text}:
5475,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se be par ke teer ya lakdi ya gaz se shikar ke barey mein puchha to aap ne farmaya ke agar uski nauk shikar ko lag jaey to kha lo lekin agar uski chaudai ki taraf se shikar ko lagey to wo na khaao kyonke wo ( موقوذة‏ yani murdaar) hai aur maine aap se kuttey ke shikar ke barey mein sawal kya to aap ne farmaya ke jisey wo tumharey liye rakhey (yani wo khud na khaaey) usey kha lo kyonke kuttey ka shikar ko pakad lena ye bhi zabah karna hai aur agar tum apne kuttey ya kutton ke sath koi doosra kutta bhi paogey aur tumhen andesha ho ke tumharey kuttey ne shikar us doosrey ke sath pakda hoga aur kutta shikar ko mar chuka ho to aisa shikar na khaao kyonke tum ne Allah ka naam ( bismillaah padh kar) apne kuttey par liya tha doosrey kuttey par nahi liya tha.
5476,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se be par ke teer ya lakdi gaz se shikar ke barey mein puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum uski nauk se shikar ko mar lo to usey khaao lekin agar uski chaudaan ki taraf se shikar ko lagey aur us se wo mar jaey to wo (murdaar) hai usey na khaao. maine sawal kya ke main apna kutta bhi) shikar ke liye) daudaataa hoon? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum apne kuttey par bismillaah padh kar shikar ke peechhey daudaao to wo shikar kha saktey ho. maine puchha aur agar wo kutta shikar mein se kha ley? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir na khaao kyonke wo shikar us ne tumharey liye nahi pakda tha, sirf apne liye pakda tha. maine puchha mein kuchh waqt apna kutta chhorta hun aur baad mein uske sath doosra kutta bhi paata hoon? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir (iska shikaar) na khaao kyonke tum ne bismillaah sirf apne kuttey par padhi hai, doosrey par nahi padhi hai."
5477,maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! ham sikhaaey huey kuttey (shikaar par) chhodtey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shikar wo sirf tumharey liye rakhey usey khaao. maine arz kya bhale hi kuttey shikar ko mar daalein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) haan ( bhale hi mar daalein! maine arz kya ke ham be par ke teer ya lakdi se shikar kartey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar unki dhaar usko zakhmi karke phaad daley to khaao lekin agar unke phal se shikar maara jaey to usey na khaao (wo murdar hai).
5478,maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Nabi ! ham ahle-kitab ke gaaun mein rahtey hain to kya ham unke bartan mein kha saktey hain? aur ham aisi zameen mein rahtey hain jahan shikar bahut hota hai. main teer kamaan se bhi shikar karta hun aur apne us kuttey se bhi jo sikhaya hua nahi hai aur us kuttey se bhi jo sikhaya hua hai to usmein se kis ka khana mere liye jaaiz hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum ne jo ahle-kitab ke bartan ka zikr kya hai to agar tumhen iske siwa koi aur bartan mil sakey to usmein na khaao lekin tumhen koi doosra bartan na miley to unke bartan ko khub dho kar usmein kha saktey ho aur jo shikar tum apni teer kamaan se karo aur) teer phainktey waqt) Allah ka naam liya ho to (uska shikaar) kha saktey ho aur jo shikar tum ne ghair sadhaaey huey kuttey se kya ho aur shikar khud zabah kya ho to usey kha saktey ho.
5479,"Abdullah-bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik shakhs ko kankari phainktey dekha to farmaya ke kankari na pheinko kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kankari phainkney se mana farmaya hai ya ( unhon-ne bayan kya ke) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kankari phainkney ko pasand nahi kartey they aur kaha ke us se na shikar kya ja sakta hai aur na dushman ko koi nuqsan pahunchaya ja sakta hai albatta ye kabhi kisi ka daant tod deti hai aur aankh phod deti hai. iske baad bhi unhon-ne us shakhs ko kankariyaan phainktey dekha to kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis tumhen suna raha hun ke aap ne kankari phainkney se mana farmaya ya kankari phainkney ko na-pasand kya aur tum ab bhi phainkey ja rahe ho, main tum se itney dinon tak kalam nahi karunga."
5480,maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne aisa kutta paalaa jo na maweshii ki hifazat ke liye hai aur na shikar karne ke liye to rozaana uski nekiyon mein se do qirat ki kami ho jati hai.
5481,"maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke shikaariyon aur maweshii ki hifazat ki gharaz ke siwa jisne kutta paalaa to uske sawab mein se rozaana 2 qirat ki kami ho jati hai."
5482,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne maweshii ki hifazat ya shikar ki gharaz ke siwa kisi aur wjah se kutta paalaa uske sawab se rozaana 2 qirat ki kami ho jati hai.
5483,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke ham log un kutton se shikar kartey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tum apne sikhaaey huey kutton ko shikar ke liye chhodtey waqt Allah ka naam letey ho to jo shikar wo tumharey liye pakad kar laaein usey khaao chahe wo shikar ko mar hi daalein. albatta agar kutta shikar mein se khud bhi kha ley to usmein ye andesha hai ke usne ye shikar khud apne liye pakda tha aur agar doosrey kuttey bhi tumharey kutton ke siwa shikar mein Sharik ho jayen to na khaao.
5484,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum ne apna kutta shikar par chhoda aur bismillaah bhi padhi aur kuttey ne shikar pakda aur usey mar daala to usey khaao aur agar us ne khud bhi kha liya to tum na khaao kyonke ye shikar us ne apne liye pakda hai aur agar doosrey kuttey jin par Allah ka naam na liya gaya ho, us kuttey ke sath shikar mein Sharik ho jayen aur shikar pakad kar mar daalein to aisa shikar na khaao kyonke tumhen malum nahi ke kis kuttey ne maara hai aur agar tum ne shikar par teer maara phir wo shikar tumhen 2 ya teen din baad mila aur is par tumharey teer ke nishan ke siwa aur koi doosra nishan nahi hai to aisa shikar khaao lekin agar wo pani mein gir gaya ho to na khaao."
5485,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke wo shikar teer se maartey hain phir 2 ya teen din par usey talash kartey hain, tab wo murda haalat mein milta hai aur uske andar unka teer ghusaa hua hota hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar to chahey to kha sakta hai."
5486,maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! main (shikaar ke liye) apna kutta chhodtey waqt bismillaah padh leta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab kutta chhodtey waqt bismillaah padh liya ho aur phir wo kutta shikar pakad ke mar daley aur khud bhi kha ley to aisa shikar na khaao kyonke ye shikar us ne khud apne liye pakda hai. maine kaha ke main kutta shikar par chhorta hun lekin iske sath doosra kutta bhi mujhey milta hai aur mujhey ye malum nahi ke kis ne shikar pakda hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aisa shikar na khaao kyonke tum ne apne kuttey par bismillaah padhi hai doosrey kuttey par nahi padhi aur maine aap se be par ke teer ya lakdi se shikar ka hukm puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar shikar nauk ki dhaar se maraa ho to kha lekin agar tu ney uske phal se usey maara hai to aisa shikar bojh se maraa hai to usey na kha .
5487,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke ham us qaum mein rahtey hain jo in kutton se shikar karti hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum apna sikhaya hua kutta chhodo aur is par Allah ka naam ley lo to agar wo kutta tumharey liye shikar laya ho to tum usey kha saktey ho lekin agar kuttey ne khud bhi kha liya ho to wo shikar na khaao kyonke andesha hai ke usne wo shikar khud apne liye pakda hai aur agar us kuttey ke sath koi doosra kutta bhi shikar mein Sharik ho jaey to phir shikar na khaao.
5488,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham ahle-kitab ke mulk mein rahtey hain aur unke bartan mein khaatey hain aur ham shikar ki zameen mein rahtey hain, jahan main apne teer se shikar karta hun aur apne sadhaaey huey kuttey se. to usmein se kya cheez hamarey liye jaaiz hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum ne jo ye kaha hai ke tum ahle-kitab ke mulk mein rahtey ho aur unke bartan mein bhi khaatey ho to agar tumhen unke bartanon ke siwa doosrey bartan mil jayen to unke bartanon mein na khaao lekin unke bartanon ke siwa doosrey bartan na milein to unhein dho kar phir unmein khaao aur tum ne shikar ki sar zameen ka zikr kya hai to jo shikar tum apne teer se maaro aur teer chalaatey waqt Allah ka naam liya ho to usey khaao aur jo shikar tum ne apne sadhaaey huey kuttey se kya ho aur is par Allah ka naam liya ho to usey khaao aur jo shikar tum ne apne bila sadhaaey kuttey se kya ho aur usey zabah bhi khud hi kya ho to usey bhi khaao ."
5489,"marruz-zohraan (Makka ke qareeb aik maqam ( mein ham ne aik khargosh ko ubhaaraa log iske peechhey daudey magar na paya phir main iske peechhey laga aur maine usey pakad liya aur usey abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas laya , unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein iska koolha aur donon raanein bhejiin to aap ne unhein qabool farma liya."
5490,wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they wo Makka ke raaste mein aik jagah par apne kuchh sathiyon ke sath jo ehram baandhey huey they peechhey reh gaey khud abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ehram se nahi they usi arse mein unhon-ne aik gorkhar dekha aur (usey shikar karne ke irade se) apne ghodey par baith gaey. iske baad apne sathiyon se (jo mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) they) kodaa maanga lekin unhon-ne deney se inkar kya phir apna neza maanga lekin usey bhi uthaney ke liye wo taiyaar nahi huey to unhon-ne wo khud uthaya aur gorkhar par hamla kya aur usey shikar kar liya phir kuchh ne iska gosht khaya aur kuchh ne khaney se inkar kya. iske baad jab wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to uska hukm puchha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye to aik khana tha jo Allah ne tumharey liye muhaiya kya tha.
5491,isi tarah riwayat kya albatta is riwayat mein ye lafz zyada hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha tha ke tumharey paas iska kuchh gosht bacha hua hai ya nahi.
5492,"main Makka aur Madina ke darmyan rastey main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha. doosrey log to ehram baandhey huey they lekin main ehram mein nahi tha aur aik ghodey par Sawar tha. main pahadon par chadhney ka bada aadi tha phir achcha maine dekha ke log lalchaaii hui nazron se koi cheez dekh rahe hain. maine jo dekha to aik gorkhar tha. maine unse puchha ke ye kya hai? logon ne kaha hamein malum nahin! maine kaha ke ye to gorkhar hai. logon ne kaha ke jo tum ne dekha hai wahi hai. main apna kodaa bhool gaya tha isliye unse kaha ke mujhey mera kodaa de do lekin unhon-ne kaha ke ham usmein tumhari koi madad nahi karengey (kyonke ham ehram ki haalat hain) maine utar kar khud kodaa uthaya aur uske peechhey se usey maaraa, wo wahin gir gaya phir maine usey zabah kya aur apne sathiyon ke paas usey lekar aaya. maine kaha ke ab utho aur usey uthaao, unhon-ne kaha ke ham usey nahi chhuengey. chunanche main hi usey utha kar unke paas laya. kuchh ne to uska gosht khaya lekin kuchh ne inkar kar diya phir maine unse kaha ke achchha main ab tumharey liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se rukney ki darkhaast karunga. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pahuncha aur aap se waqia bayan kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey paas usmein se kuchh baqi bacha hai? maine arz kya, ji haan. farmaya khaao kyonke ye aik khana hai jo Allah Taala ne tum ko khilaaya hai."
5493,"ham jange-khabat mein Sharik they, hamarey ameer abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) they. ham sab bhook se betaab they ke samandar ne aik murda machhli bahar phenkii . aisi machhli dekhi nahi gaee thi. usey anbar kehtey they, ham ne wo machhli pandarah din tak khaaii. phir abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski aik haddi lekar ( khadi kar di ( to wo itni unchi thi ke aik sawar uske nichey se guzar gaya."
5494,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen so sawar rawaana kiye. hamarey ameer abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) they. hamein Quraish ke tijarati qaafile ki naql w harkat par nazar rakhni thi phir (khaanaa khatm ho janey ki wjah se) ham sakht bhook aur faaqe ki haalat mein they. naubat yahan tak pahunch gaee thi ke ham Salam ke patey (khabt) kha kar waqt guzaartey they. isi liye us muhim ka naam ''jaishul-Khabat'' pad gaya aur samandar ne aik machhli bahar daal di. jiska naam anbar tha. ham ne usey aadhey mahina tak khaya aur uski charbi tel ke taur par apne jism par malii jis se hamarey jism tandurust ho gaey. bayan kya ke phir abu Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne uski aik paslii ki haddi lekar khadi ki to aik sawar uske nichey se guzar gaya. hamarey sath aik sahib (Qais-bin-Sa'd bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu)) they jab ham bahut zyada bhookey huey to unhon-ne ek ke baad doosrey teen oont zabah kar diye. baad mein abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein us se mana kar diya.
5495,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath saat (7) ya chh jangon mein Sharik huey, ham aap ke sath tiddii khaatey they. Sufiyan , abu-Awana aur Israel ne abu-Ya'foor se bayan kya aur unse ibne-abii-Aufii ne, saat (7) jang ke lafz riwayat kiye."
5496,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : ya Rasulullah ! ham ahle-kitab ke mulk mein rahtey hain aur unke bartanon mein khaatey hain aur ham shikar ki zameen mein rahtey hain aur main apne teer kamaan se bhi shikar karta hun aur sadhaaey huey kuttey se aur be-sadhaaey kuttey se bhi ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum ne jo ye kaha hai ke tum ahle-kitab ke mulk mein rahtey ho to unke bartanon mein na khaya karo. albatta agar zarurat ho aur khana hi pad jaey to unhein khub dho liya karo aur jo tum ne ye kaha hai ke tum shikar ki zameen mein rahtey ho to jo shikar tum apne teer kamaan se karo aur is par Allah ka naam liya ho to usey khaao aur jo shikar tum ne apne sadhaaey huey kuttey se kya ho aur is par Allah ka naam liya ho wo bhi khaao aur jo shikar tum ne apne bila sadhaaey huey kuttey se kya ho aur usey khud zabah kya ho usey khaao.
5497,fateh khaibar ki Sham ko logon ne aag roshan ki to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke ye aag tum logon ne kis liye roshan ki hai? logon ne bataya ke gadhey ka gosht hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haandiyon mein kuchh (gadhey ka gosht) hai usey phenk do aur haandiyon ko tod daalo. aik shakhs ne khadey ho kar kaha handi mein jo kuchh (gosht wghaira) hai usey ham phenk dein aur bartan dho lein? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye bhi kar saktey ho.
5498,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maqam zul-Hulaifa mein they ke (ham) log bhook aur faaqe mein mubtala ho gaey phir hamein (ghaneemat mein) oont aur bakriyan miliin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sabse peechhey they. logon ne jaldi ki bhook ki shiddat ki wjah se (aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke tashrif laney se pahley hi ghaneemat ke janwaron ko zabah kar liyaa) aur haandiyaan pakney ke liye chadhaa diin phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya aur haandiyaan ulat di gain phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghaneemat ki taqseem ki aur das bakriyon ko aik oont ke barabar qarar diya. unmein se aik oont bhag gaya. qaum ke paas ghodon ki kami thi log us oont ke peechhey daudey lekin us ne sab ko thakaa diya. aakhir aik shakhs ne is par teer ka nishana kya to Allah Taala ne usey rok diya is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un janwaron mein jangliyon ki tarah wahshat hoti hai. isliye jab koi janwar bhadak kar bhag jaey to iske sath aisa hi kya karo. abaaya ne bayan kya ke mere dada (Raafe'-bin-Khadeej (rz)) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke hamein andesha hai ke kal hamara dushman se muqaabla hoga aur hamarey paas chhuriyaan nahi hain kya ham (dhaardaar) lakdi se zabah kar lein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo cheez bhi khoon baha de aur (zabah kartey waqt) janwar par Allah ka naam liya ho to usey khaao albatta (zabah karne wala aala) daant aur naakhun na hona chahiye daant isliye nahi ke ye haddi hai (aur haddi se zabah karna jaaiz nahi hai) aur naakhun ka isliye nahi ke habshi log unko chhuri ki jagah istemal kartey hain.
5499,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Zaid-bin Amr-bin-Naufal se maqam balad ke nashebii hisse mein mulaqat hui. ye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil honey se pahley ka zamana hai. aap ne wo dastar-khuwaan jis mein gosht tha jisey un logon ne aap ki ziyaafat ke liye pesh kya tha magar un par zabah ke waqt buton ka naam liya gaya tha, aap ne usey Zaid-bin Amr ke samney wapas farma diya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum jo janwar apne buton ke naam par zabah kartey ho main unhein nahi khaataa, mein sirf usi janwar ka gosht khata hun jis par (zabah kartey waqt) Allah ka naam liya gaya ho."
5500,"ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik martaba qurbani ki. kuchh logon ne eid ki Namaz se pahley hi qurbani kar li thi. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (namaz padh kar) wapas tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke logon ne apni qurbaniyan Namaz se pahley hi zabah kar li hain phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis shakhs ne Namaz se pahley qurbani zabah kar li ho, usey chahiye ke uski jagah dusri zabah karey aur jisne Namaz padhney se pahley na zabah ki ho usey chahiye ke Allah ke naam par zabah kare."
5501,unke ghar aik londi Sala pahaadii par bakriyan charaayaa karti thi (charaatey waqt aik martaba) us ne dekha ke aik bakri marney wali hai. chunanche usne aik patthar tod kar us se bakri zabah kar di to Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne ghar walon se kaha ke usey us waqt tak na khana jab tak main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska hukm na poochh aaoon ya (unhon-ne ye kaha ke) main kisi ko bhejoon jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se masla poochh aaey phir wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey ya kisi ko bheja aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske khaney ki ijazat bakhshii.
5502,"Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki aik londi us pahaadii par jo ''baazaar madnii'' main hai aur jiska naam Sala hai, bakriyan charaayaa karti thi. aik bakri marney ke qareeb ho gaee to usne aik patthar tod kar us se bakri ko zabah kar liya, phir logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey khaney ki ijazat ata farmai."
5503,unhon-ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! hamarey paas chhuri nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo (dhaar daar) cheez khoon baha de aur is par Allah ka naam ley liya gaya ho to (is se zabah kya hua jaanwar) kha saktey ho lekin naakhun aur daant se zabah na kya gaya ho kyonke naakhun habshiyon ki chhuri hai aur daant haddi hai aur aik oont bhag gaya to (teer mar kar) usey rok liya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ye oont bhi janglii janwaron ki tarah bhadak uthtey hain isliye jo tumharey qaabu se bahar ho jaey iske sath aisa hi kya karo.
5504,"aik aurat ne bakri patthar se zabah kar li thi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske barey mein puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske khaney ka hukm farmaya aur Leis ne bayan kya, unse Naafe ne bayan kya, unhon-ne qabila Ansar ke aik shakhs ko suna ke unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko khabar di Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ki aik londi thi phir usi hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
5505,Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki aik londi Sala pahaadii par bakriyan charaayaa karti thi. rewad mein se aik bakri marney lagi to usne usey marney se pahley patthar se zabah kar diya phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq puchha gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey khaao.
5506,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khaao yani (aisey janwar ko jisey aisi dhaardaar cheez se zabah kya gaya ho) jo khoon baha de. siwaae daant aur naakhun ke (yani unse zabah karna durust nahi hai).
5507,(gaaun ke) kuchh log hamarey yahan gosht (bechney) latey hain aur hamein malum nahi ke unhon-ne is par Allah ka naam bhi (zabah kartey waqt) liya tha ya nahi? aap ne farmaya ke tum un par khaatey waqt Allah ka naam liya karo aur kha liya karo. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke ye log abhi Islam mein naey-naey dakhil huey they. iski mutabiat (pairavi) Ali ne darawardi se ki aur uski mutabiat (pairavi) abu-Khalid aur Tafaawii ne ki.
5508,ham khaibar ke qil'ey ka muhaasra kiye huey they ke aik shakhs ne aik thailaa phainkaa jis main (yahoodiyon ke zabiha ki) charbi thi. main is par jhaptaa ke utha loon lekin mud ke jo dekha to peechhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif farma they. main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh kar sharma gaya. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke (aayat mein) ( طَعامهم ( se murad ahle-kitab ka zabah karda janwar hai.
5509,"maine kaha : ya Rasulullah! kal hamara muqaabla dushman se hoga aur hamarey paas chhuriyaan nahi hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir jaldi kar lo ya (iske bajaey) ( أرن ( kaha yani jaldi kar lo jo aala khoon baha de aur zabiha par Allah ka naam liya gaya ho to usey khaao. albatta daant aur naakhun na hona chahiye aur uski wjah bhi bata dun. daant to haddi hai aur naakhun habshiyon ki chhuri hai. aur hamein ghaneemat mein oont aur bakriyan miliin unmein se aik oont bidak kar bhag padaa to aik sahib ne teer se mar kar gira liya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye oont bhi kabhi-kabhi janglii janwaron ki tarah bidaktey hain, isliye agar unmein se bhi koi tumharey qaabu se bahar ho jaey to iske sath aisa hi karo."
5510,unse Asma binte- abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein aik ghoda qurbaan kya aur usey khaayaa.
5511,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein ham ne aik ghoda zabah kya aur iska gosht khaya us waqt ham Madina mein they.
5512,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein ham ne aik ghodey ko nehar kya (iske seeney ke uper ke hisse mein chhuri mar kar) phir usey khaayaa. iski mutabiat (pairavi) Wakee aur ibne-Uena ne Hisham se ( nehar . Mina (ke zikr ke sath ki.
5513,"main Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Hakam-bin-Ayyoob ke yahan gaya, unhon-ne wahan chand ladkon ko ya naujawaanon ko dekha ke aik murghi ko baandh kar is par teer ka nishana laga rahe hain to unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zinda janwar ko baandh kar maarney se mana farmaya hai."
5514,wo Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey they ke wo Yahya-bin-Saeed ke yahan tashrif ley gaey. Yahya ki aulad mein aik bachcha aik murghi baandh kar is par teer ka nishana laga raha tha. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) murghi ke paas gaey aur usey khol liya phir murghi ko aur bachchey ko apne sath laey aur Yahya se kaha ke apne bachcha ko mana kar do ke us janwar ko baandh kar na maarey kyonke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai aap ne kisi janglii janwar ya kisi bhi janwar ko baandh kar jaan se maarney se mana farmaya hai.
5515,main ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha wo chand jawaanon ya (ye kaha ke) chand aadmiyon ke paas se guzrey jinhoney aik murghi baandh rakhi thi aur is par teer ka nishana laga rahe they jab unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha to wahan se bhag gaey. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ye kon kar raha tha? aisa karne walon par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne laanat bheji hai. uski mutabiat (pairavi) Sulaiman ne Shoba se ki hai.
5516,"maine Abdullah-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rahzanii karne aur musla karne se mana farmaya hai."
5517,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko murghi khaatey dekha hai.
5518,"ham se abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they ham main aur us qabila jurm mein bhai-chara tha phir khana laya gaya jis mein murghi ka gosht bhi tha, haaziriin mein aik shakhs surkh rang ka betha hua tha lekin wo khaney mein Sharik nahi hua, abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha ke tum bhi Sharik ho jao. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko iska gosht khaatey huey dekha hai. usne kaha ke maine murghi ko gandagi khaatey dekha tha usi waqt se mujhey us se ghin aaney lagi hai aur maine qism kha li hai ke ab iska gosht nahi khaaunga. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Sharik ho jao main tumhen khabar deta hun ya unhon-ne kaha ke main tum se bayan karta hun ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein qabila ash'ar ke chand logon ko sath lekar hazir hua, main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aaya to aap khafa they aap sadqe ke oont taqseem farma rahe they. usi waqt ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawari ke liye oont ka sawal kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qism kha li ke aap hamein sawari ke liye oont nahi dengey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere paas tumharey liye sawari ka koi janwar nahi hai. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ghaneemat ke oont laey gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Ash-ari kahan hain, Ash-ari kahan hain? bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein panch safaid kohan waley oont de diye. thodi der tak to ham khamosh rahe lekin phir maine apne sathiyon se kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni qism bhool gaey hain aur agar ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aap ki qism ke barey mein ghaafil rakha to ham kabhi falaah nahi pa sakengey. chunanche ham aap ki khidmat mein wapas aaey aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! ham ne aap se sawari ke oont aik martaba maangey they, to aap ne hamein sawari ke liye koi janwar na dene ki qism kha li thi hamarey khayal mein aap apni qism bhool gaey hain Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bila shubah Allah hi ki wo zaat hai jisne tumhen sawari ke liye janwar ata farmaya, Allah ki qasam! agar Allah ne chaha to kabhi aisa nahi ho sakta ke main koi qism kha loon aur phir baad mein mujh par waazeh ho jaey ke iske siwa dusri cheez us se behtar hai aur phir wahi mein na karun jo behtar hai, main qism tod doonga aur wahi karunga jo behtar hoga aur qism todney ka kaffara ada kar doonga."
5519,ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein aik ghoda zabah kya aur usey khaayaa.
5520,jange-khaibar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne gadhey ka gosht khaney ki manaahii farma di thi aur ghodey ka gosht khaney ki rukhsat di thi.
5521,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jang khaibar ke mauqe par paaltu gadhon ke gosht ki manaahii kar di thi.
5522,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne paaltu gadhon ke gosht ki manaahii ki thi. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) ibne-Mubarak ne ki thi, unse Naafe ne aur abu-Usama ne bayan kya, unse Ubaidullah ne aur unse Salim ne isi tarah se bayan kya."
5523,Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jange-khaibar ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mutaa aur paaltu gadhon ke gosht ke khaney se mana farma diya tha.
5524,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jang khaibar ke mauqe par gadhon ke gosht khaney se mana farma diya tha aur ghodon ke liye rukhsat farma di thi.
5525,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne gadhey ka gosht khaney se mana farma diya tha.
5526,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne gadhey ka gosht khaney se mana farma diya tha.
5527,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne paaltu gadhey ka gosht khana haram qarar diya tha. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Zubaidi aur Aqeel ne ibne-Shahab se ki hai. Maalik, Ma'mar, maajishoon, Yunus aur ibne- Ishaq ne Zohri se bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne har phaad kar khaney waley darindey ka gosht khaney se mana farmaya hai."
5528,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik sahib aaey aur arz kya ke maine gadhey ka gosht kha liya hai phir doosrey sahib aaey aur kaha ke maine gadhey ka gosht kha liya hai phir teesrey sahib aaey aur kaha ke gadhey khatm ho gaey. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik manaadii ke zariey logon mein elaan karaya ke Allah Taala aur uske rasool tumhen paaltu gadhon ka gosht khaney se mana kartey hain kyonke wo napak hain chunanche usi waqt haandiyaan ulat di gain halanke wo ( gadhey ke) gosht se josh mar rahi thin.
5529,logon ka khayal hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne paaltu gadhon ka gosht khaney se mana kya tha? unhon-ne kaha ke Hakam-bin-Amr Ghifari (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Basra mein yahi bataya tha lekin ilm ke samandar Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se inkar kya aur (istidlaal mein) is aayat ki tilawat ki قل لا أجد فيما أوحي إلى محرما .
5530,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne har phaad khaney waley darindon ka gosht khaney se mana kya tha. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Younus, Ma'mar, ibne-Uena aur maajishoon ne Zohri ki sanad se ki hai."
5531,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik mari hui bakri ke qareeb se guzrey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum ne iske chamdey se fayda kyon nahi uthaayaa? logon ne kaha ke ye to mari hui hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sirf iska khana haram kya gaya hai.
5532,"maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik marey huey bakrey ke paas se guzrey to farmaya ke iske maalikon ko kya ho gaya hai agar wo iske chamdey ko kaam mein latey (to behtar hotaa)."
5533,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo zakhmi bhi Allah ke rastey mein zakhmi ho gaya ho usey qiyamat ke din us haalat mein uthaya jaeyga ke uske zakhm se jo khoon jari hoga uska rang to khoon hi jaisa hoga magar usmein mashk jaisi khushbu hogi.
5534,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nek aur burey dost ki misal mashk sath rakhney waley aur bhattii dhonkney waley ki si hai (jiske paas mashk hai aur tum uski mohabbat mein ho) wo usmein se ya tumhen kuchh tohfe ke taur par dega ya tum us se khareed sakogey ya (kam az kam) tum uski umda khushbu se to mehfooz ho hi sakogey aur bhattii dhonkney wala ya tumharey kapdey (bhattii ki aag se) jalaa dega ya tumhen uske paas se aik na-gawar badbudar dhuaan pahunchega.
5535,ham ne aik khargosh ka peechhaa kya. ham marruz-zohraan mein they. log iske peechhey daudey aur thak gaey phir maine usey pakad liya aur usey abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas laya. unhon-ne usey zabah kya aur uske donon koolhey ya (raawii ne bayan kya ke) uski donon raanein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas bhejiin aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein qabool farmaya.
5536,maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke saahina main khud nahi khata lekin usey haram bhi nahi qarar detaa.
5537,"wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Ummul-Momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar gaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhunaa hua saahina laya gaya aap ne uski taraf hath badhaya lekin kuchh aurton ne kaha ke aap jo khana dekh rahe hain iske mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bata do, aurton ne kaha ke ye saahina hai ya Rasulullah ! chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath kheench liya. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! kya ye haram hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi lekin chunkey ye hamarey mulk mein nahi paya jata isliye tabeeat us se inkar karti hai. Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir maine usey apni taraf kheench liya aur khaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dekh rahe they."
5538,"aik choohaa ghi mein pad kar mar gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska hukm puchha gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke choohey ko aur uske charon taraf se ghi ko phenk 2 aur baqi ghi ko khaao. Sufiyan se kaha gaya ke Mamar us hadis ko Zohri se bayan kartey hain ke unse Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ke maine ye hadis Zohri se sirf Ubaidullah se bayan kartey suni hai ke unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne, unse Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur maine ye hadis unse bahut baar suni hai."
5539,"agar koi janwar choohaa ya koi aur jamey huey ya ghair jamey huey ghi ya tel mein pad jaey to iske mutaalliq kaha ke hamein ye hadis pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne choohey ke mutaalliq jo ghi mein mar gaya tha, hukm diya ke usey aur uske charon taraf se ghi nikal kar phenk diya jaey aur phir baqi ghi khaya gaya. hamein ye hadis Ubaidullaah-bin-Abdullaah ki sanad se pahunchi hai."
5540,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us choohey ka hukm puchha gaya jo ghi mein gir gaya ho. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke choohey ko aur uske charon taraf se ghi ko phenk do phir baqi ghi kha lo.
5541,"wo chehrey par nishan lagaaney ko na-pasand kartey they aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chehrey par maarney se mana kya hai. Ubaidullah bin-Musa ke sath is hadis ko Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne bhi riwayat kya, kaha ham ko Amr bin-Muhammad Anqarii ne khabar di, unhon-ne Hanzala se."
5542,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apne bhai ( Abdullah-bin-Ubai Talha nau-maulood (new born)) ko laya taake aap uski tehneek farma dein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt oonton ke baadey mein tashrif rakhtey they. maine dekha ke aap aik bakri ko dagh rahe they (Shoba ne kaha ke) main samajhta hun ke (Hishaam ne) kaha ke iske kanon ko dagh rahe they.
5543,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke kal hamara dushman se muqaabla hoga aur hamarey paas chhuriyaan nahi hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo aala khoon baha de aur) janwaron ko zabah kartey waqt) is par Allah ka naam liya gaya ho usey khaao basharte ke zabah ka aala daant aur naakhun na ho aur main uski wjah tumhen bataunga . daant to haddi hai aur naakhun habshiyon ki chhuri hai aur jaldi karne waley log aagey badh gaey they aur ghaneemat par qabza kar liya tha lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) peechhey ke sahaba ke sath they chunanche ( aagey pahunchne walon ne janwar zabah karke ( haandiyaan pakney ke liye chadhaa diin lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ulat dene ka hukm farmaya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghaneemat logon ke darmyan taqseem ki. us taqseem mein aik oont ko das bakriyon ke barabar aap ne qarar diya tha phir aagey ke logon se aik oont bidak kar bhag gaya. logon ke paas ghodey nahi they phir aik shakhs ne us oont par teer maara aur Allah Taala ne usey rok liya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye janwar bhi kabhi wahshii janwaron ki tarah bidakney lagtey hain. isliye jab unmein se koi aisa karey to tum bhi unke sath aisa hi karo."
5544,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they. aik oont bidak kar bhag padaa, phir aik aadmi ne teer se usey maara aur Allah Taala ne usey rok diya. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye oont bhi kabhii-kabhii janglii janwaron ki tarah bidaktey hain, isliye unmein se jo tumharey qaabu se bahar ho jaaein, unke sath aisa hi kya karo. Raafe ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham aksar ghazawaat aur doosrey safaron mein rahtey hain aur janwar zabah karna chahtey hain lekin hamarey paas chhuriyaan nahi hotiin. farmaya ke dekh liya karo jo aala khoon baha de ya (aap ne bajaey ( نهر ( ke) ( أنهر ( farmaya aur is par Allah ka naam liya gaya ho to usey khaao. albatta daant aur naakhun na ho kyonke daant haddi hai aur naakhun habsh walon ki chhuri hai."
